videos.description: Louisville's Quentin Snider makes the fastbreak layup after Deng Adel forces the turnover.
videos.headline: Louisville out and running early against UNC

videos.description: Quentin Snider finds Anas Mahmoud with the lob as Louisville leads North Carolina early.
videos.headline: Louisville's Mahmoud catches lob for alley-oop

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson's shot clanks off the back of the rim but drops for the 3-pointer as against Louisville.
videos.headline: UNC's Jackson gets friendly roll on 3-pointer

videos.description: Louisville's Deng Adel throws down the emphatic one-handed dunk in the first half against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Deng Adel flies through the lane for one-handed dunk

videos.description: Louisville coach Rick Pitino has to be held back by staff at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Pitino gets into shouting match heading to locker room

videos.description: Theo Pinson makes the tough scoop shot as North Carolina gets off to a good start in the second half against Louisville.
videos.headline: UNC's Pinson avoids the defense with the scoop

videos.description: Anas Mahmoud beats the defense down the floor and makes the athletic bucket for Louisville.
videos.headline: Louisville's Mahmoud catches lob for the tough finish

videos.description: Louisville's Donovan Mitchell is keeping things close against UNC with his 3-point shooting.
videos.headline: Mitchell getting hot from behind the arc

videos.description: Justin Jackson finds Tony Bradley underneath for the layup as North Carolina extends their lead over Louisville.
videos.headline: Bradley's layup has UNC pulling away against Louisville

videos.description: Justin Jackson finishes with left hand as UNC continues to outplay Louisville in the second half.
videos.headline: Jackson's runner extends lead for Tar Heels

videos.description: Justin Jackson continues his strong night against Louisville by making the deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Jackson can't help but smile after nailing 3-pointer

videos.description: Justin Jackson had a big night to lead the Tar Heels over Louisville.
videos.headline: Breaking down No. 8 North Carolina's win over No. 7 Louisville

videos.description: Rick Pitino explains his verbal altercation incident with a Tar Heels fan who was later ejected from the game while Roy Williams apologizes to Pitino, saying he hopes that never happens again at North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (UNC was the 'classiest place' for Pitino until he met one fan) 2017/02/22 HSV ENHL

videos.headline: UNC the 'classiest place' for Pitino until he met one fan
